- Decision: Base work on `origin/afk/run-20260720-084338` rather than cherry-picking individual commits. Why: the 4 commits sit on top of a full app tree with all predecessors (#103–#107) merged; extracting them onto the docs-only `capstone/opencode-273` is impossible without the entire app tree.
- Decision: Treat existing 4-commit implementation as the primary artifact to validate, not reimplement. Why: the code is already complete, tested, and reviewed per the comment thread; reimplementation would duplicate effort with no quality gain.

